{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回\"救人害己\"承接前章，楚留香、胡铁花、姬冰雁、小潘及石驼继续在沙漠中行进。胡铁花因轻信伪装者而上当，姬冰雁虽未责备却暗中将被毒针污染的水倒掉，揭示了暗器的致命毒性。楚留香发现敌人使用的针筒暗器精巧程度超越昔年\"九天十地天魔神针\"，推断制造者可能是蜀中唐门掌门、江南九曲塘朱老先生或第四位未知高手。姬冰雁透露百里外有秘密水源，但到达后发现水源已干涸，众人陷入绝境。此时远处出现四名疯狂奔逃的彭门五虎成员，他们挥刀砍杀虚空，疑似被沙漠中的可怕事物逼疯。胡铁花认出彭云的五虎断门刀法，决定出手相救，章末悬念迭起。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "原来这也用了易容术，而且手法不在楚留香之下，沙漠里也有这样的人才，我们真想不到。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来这两人白送了性命，并没害到咱们，咱们还是有水喝。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你这是做什么?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "暗器有毒，毒已溶入水里，水自然喝不得了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已找着了他们射暗器的针筒，构造之精巧，竟似还在昔年名震天下的'九天十地，天魔神针'之上，我实在想不出江湖中谁能造得出这样的暗器?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这且留到晚上再说，现在还是赶紧走吧!",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "这全是我不好，是我爱多事，是我瞎了眼，你……你为什么不骂我?不说话?你痛骂我一顿，我反会好受些。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你要我骂你?",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你不骂，你就是混蛋!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我为何要骂你?救人总是好事，何况，瞎了眼的不只是你一个，上当的也不只是你——个。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这死公鸡并不如你想像中的可恶，是么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这实在是我生平所见到的最可怕的几种暗器之一，我想，世上只有三个人能造得出这样的暗器。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "三个人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "第一个是蜀中唐门的掌门人。第二个是江南九曲塘的朱老先生，这两人自然绝不会到沙漠来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错……还有一个人呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "还有一个就是我，这暗器自然也不会是我造的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你虽只知道三个人，但我认为必定有第四个人的，只不过这人是谁，你我都不知道而已。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "能造出这样的暗器并不可怕，可怕的是，这人竟能令他手下心甘情愿地为他而死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你认为这绝不是你那对头黑珍珠?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "绝不是，黑珍珠没有这么强，也没有这么狠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你想这会是什么人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "我想，这人或许是自中原出关的一个极厉害的黑道朋友，或许是沙漠中流寇的首领，他并不是冲着我楚留香来的，也不是冲着你姬冰雁来的，他只是将我们当做一队'肥羊'，要从我们身上刮些油水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "有你在，我从来没有怕会被渴死。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道就在百里外，有个秘密的水源，明天日落之前，我们就可以赶到那里，我方才没有说，只因我想让胡铁花着着急。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水只有这么多了，你们可以现在一口气喝下去，也可以留着。反正这点水最多也不过只能支持两三天。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "这是你自己留着的水，我不喝。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你莫和姬冰雁赌气，和他赌气是会上当的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我和他赌什么气，昨天晚上，我已听到他今天能找到水，只不过我自己还有一壶酒，我为什么喝这淡出鸟来的淡水。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "是你要石驼停下来的，是么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你只一挥手，他就懂你的意思了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "但你却说他又瞎又聋，他怎么能看得见?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我自有方法让他知道我的意思。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你有什么见鬼的法子?为何不说出来?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你真的瞧不出?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "王八蛋才瞧得出。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你用一颗小石子来传达你的命令，你若要队伍停下，便用石子打石驼的左肩，若要队伍走，就打他的右肩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这法子并非只有王八蛋才瞧得出的，是么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不是王八蛋，我是，我现在发觉我实在未见得比王八蛋聪明多少。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "这里有水?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "水在哪里，我怎地瞧不见?难道我不但脑袋不灵，连眼睛也不灵了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "听说沙漠里有许多秘密的水源，是藏在地下的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你莫说了，我承认我什么都不懂好吗?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来不是很聪明的吗?怎地和这两人在一起，就变成了呆子，莫非是被人传染上呆病。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小潘",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "胡爷若真的染上了呆病，那一定是我传过去的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "你怎会传给他，他比你还要呆得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你再想想，有没有弄错地方?",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不信任我?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小潘",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "地下的水源，有时会忽然干枯，有时会忽然改道，这是老天爷开的玩笑，什么人也没法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你莫怪我，我的……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "我知道你的心情，我若是你，不但也会拿你出气，说不定发的脾气更大。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "不错，一个人难受时，不拿好朋友出气拿谁出气，好朋友若不能谅解他，谁还能谅解他?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小潘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "小人斗胆插嘴说句话……谁若能交着楚爷和胡爷这样的朋友，他可实在是这世上最运的人了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "此时此刻，咱们绝不能妄动，先静观待变。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是怎么回事?这些人在逃避什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "沙漠上常会有一些诡秘之极的事，只要不惹到咱们身上，咱们最好还是装做瞎子，只当没瞧见。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "若是惹到咱们身上的呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人莫非瞧见了鬼么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小潘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我曾听说沙漠中有种隐形的恶魔，专门吃人的心肝，他们莫非……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "不许胡说。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是彭家刀法。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "我也看出来了，彭家的人，怎会变成这样子的?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错!这竟真的是五虎断门刀!而且瞧这四个人的刀法功力，一定是彭家子弟中有头有脸的人物。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "五虎断门刀素来不传外姓，这四人多半就是彭云的子侄，彭门五虎中的兄弟，这大胡子也许就是彭一虎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "彭门五虎现在是否已继承了彭云的镖局?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "若是如此，他们必是走镖而来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小潘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一定是这样，在沙漠上只有走镖的人，才不骑骆驼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彭云为人不错，我不能眼看着他儿子发狂而死，我要去救他。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 345
    }
  ],
